{"tid":1814833,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 黃色M巾","createTime":"2020-01-07T05:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T11:54:56.000Z","uid":227404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4460ef4ddd5f373ea878466aa29e20fb02c1d1","tid":1814833,"uid":227404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:49:01.000Z","msg":"出街買M巾 護墊 香港常用品牌好多都係MIC (Made in China) / MIPRC (Made in People's Republic of China)<br />\n<br />\nKotex 高潔絲9成9都係上海製<br />\n樂而雅部分衞生巾包裝上寫明「日本製造」，但其它系列就無寫明，但睇返公司都係中國廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWhisper 護舒寶用緊中國代言人<br />\n而且護舒寳衞生巾大部分中國製造，而液體衞生巾系列係唯一由北美加拿大進口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位絲打有無好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外強烈推介各位絲打考慮用棉條，生活從此爽心又愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要都係台灣製造 歐美製造<br />\n連登有集中帖討論棉條使用心得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6421493970269302dbe31ae3a3ea68bfcf482b90","tid":1814833,"uid":10593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ff452ebbad567a685b9d9380e625d28192f02e","tid":1814833,"uid":17812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSUryCD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSUryCD.png&h=37715939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用開made in japan<br />\n閪位夠窄, 唔會刮損閪邊, 好撚舒服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c99dbb5509451424001b0f799f3447eec473a9","tid":1814833,"uid":227404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9ff452ebbad567a685b9d9380e625d28192f02e","tid":1814833,"uid":17812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://